column2: SELECT p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.r, t.z as photoz, t.zErr as photozErr, s.z as specz, s.zErr as speczErr, t.type, SQRT (POWER (( (#-t.ra) *cos ((t.dec) * (#/#) )) , #) + (POWER ((#-t.dec) , #) )) as angsep INTO mydb.A1#_neighbors1_zall FROM dbo.Photoz as t, mydb.A1#_neighbors1 as p, dbo.SpecObj as s where t.objID = p.objID and s.targetObjID = p.objID
